OL,3,CLack of support leaves record number
OL,4,Cof adoptive families in crisis
OL,6,FOne man told ITV News how a lack of
OL,7,Fprofessional support after being
OL,8,Fadopted as a child made his life 'very
OL,9,Fdifficult' at times, Social Affairs
OL,10,FCorrespondent Sarah Corker reports
OL,12,FMartin Griffiths was one when he was
OL,13,Fadopted by a family in Wales.
OL,15,FWhile he has happy memories of his
OL,16,Fchildhood, he recalls how his school
OL,17,Fyears were marred by bullying and how
OL,18,Fteachers lacked the understanding or
OL,19,Ftraining to support him.
