OL,6,FHe said: "Other kids used to say to
OL,7,Fme, 'your real mum didn't want you.'
OL,8,FChildren can be really horrible, it's
OL,9,Fdifficult to discuss adoption with
OL,10,Fpeople who don't understand, let alone
OL,11,Fwhen you are in Year 5 at school."
OL,13,FHis two biological sisters were later
OL,14,Fadopted by the same family, but then
OL,15,Ftragedy struck when their adoptive
OL,16,Ffather died while the siblings were
OL,17,Fstill very young.
