OL,6,F'It's difficult to discuss adoption
OL,7,Fwith people who don't understand, and
OL,8,Fespecially when you're in Year 5 in
OL,9,Fprimary school,' Martin Griffiths told
OL,10,FITV News
OL,12,FMartin recalls the void of any
OL,13,Fprofessional support; his adoptive
OL,14,Fmother left to bring up the children
OL,15,Falone, and one of his sisters
OL,16,Fstruggling with complex mental health
OL,17,Fproblems.
OL,19,F"Growing up, it was very difficult to
OL,20,Fdeal with life at times," he said.
