OL,6,F"One of my sisters had complex needs -
OL,7,Fshe was labelled as 'the naughty
OL,8,Fchild, the difficult one' at school.
OL,10,F"It was only later in life that she
OL,11,Fwas diagnosed with ADHD, dyspraxia and
OL,12,Fautism."
OL,14,FMore adoptive families are in crisis
OL,15,Fthan ever before due to the cost-of-
OL,16,Fliving, the aftermath of the Covid-19
OL,17,Fpandemic and stretched public
OL,18,Fservices, according to a new survey by
OL,19,FAdoption UK.
