OL,6,FThe charity says that while adoption
OL,7,Fremains a vital intervention for
OL,8,Fchildren who cannot safely grow up
OL,9,Fwith their birth family, support
OL,10,Fservices for adoptees "must be
OL,11,Freliable and accessible, especially at
OL,12,Fthe toughest times, and must not
OL,13,Fdisappear when people turn 18".
OL,15,FAdoption UK CEO Emily Frith said:
OL,16,F"When record numbers of families say
OL,17,Fthey're in crisis it's time to listen
OL,18,Fand to take urgent action.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/13
