OL,6,F"We must fix the disconnect with other
OL,7,Fservices such as mental health and
OL,8,Feducation."
OL,10,FIn Lincolnshire, we heard from another
OL,11,Ffamily whose story is all too familiar.
OL,13,FAlison Woodhead, Director of Public
OL,14,FAffairs at Adoption UK, told ITV News
OL,15,Fthat a 're-set' in attitudes is needed
OL,16,Fto ensure 'lifelong support' is
OL,17,Foffered to adopted children and 'not
OL,18,Fjust at the beginning'
