OL,6,FLiv was adopted when she was three-
OL,7,Fyears-old. Now a teenager, she's been
OL,8,Fbullied physically and verbally at
OL,9,Fschool and struggles with her mental
OL,10,Fhealth describing feeling like she's
OL,11,F"existing" instead of living.
OL,13,FThe family is desperate for help, but
OL,14,Ffelt let down by teachers and social
OL,15,Fworkers.
OL,17,F"It's soul destroying, it doesn't have
OL,18,Fto be like this," Louise said.
