OL,6,F"There's a lot of support initially,
OL,7,Fbut as life goes on and children
OL,8,Fbecome adopted, that just drops away
OL,9,Fas if there's nothing."
OL,11,FLouise described how her daughter's
OL,12,Fearly life was disrupted by different
OL,13,Ffoster care placements and a lack of
OL,14,Femotional support.
OL,16,FProblems then escalated in secondary
OL,17,Fschool as severe bullying "was dealt
OL,18,Fwith in a terrible way by the school".
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/13
