OL,6,F"It has been heartbreaking and
OL,7,Ffrustrating. It's been hard to get
OL,8,Fpast the gate keepers of the school,
OL,9,Fand get to someone who would
OL,10,Funderstand and listen," Louise said.
OL,12,F"We should train all staff at every
OL,13,Flevel, in every school, in how to be
OL,14,Fmore sensitive and trauma-informed
OL,15,Fwith correct strategies.
OL,17,F"It should be in initial teacher
OL,18,Ftraining."
OL,20,FIn the UK, more than 3,000 children
OL,21,Fare adopted every year.
